        <subtitle>The ECB Haircut</subtitle>
        <chapter>
          <title>ECB measures for Greek</title>
          <paragraph>The European Central Bank's measures—called “haircut”—imposed on the Greek government cause a lot of negative effects to the Greek population and also to it's investors.</paragraph>
        </chapter>
