        <chapter>
          <title>Greek needs less debt</title>
          <paragraph>In the first bailout International Monetary Fund cut Greece debt by €100 billion. But this is not so much for the Greece financial crisis, in fact they will ask another debt cut in the next meeting, because the situation is difficult.</paragraph>
        </chapter>
